    {
      "id": "github:einstein_gravity::general_relativity__einstein_field_equations",
      "type": "claim",
      "visibility": "public",
      "content": "爱因斯坦场方程：引力不是超距力，而是质能分布导致的时空弯曲。   G_μ ν + Λ g_μ ν = (8 π G)/c^4 T_μ ν   左端   G_μ ν （Einstein 张量）描述时空曲率，   右端   T_μ ν （能动张量）描述物质能量分布，   Λ   为宇宙学常数。",
      "content_hash": "37bbbb1faf28d2bbad2b0fe55f12eef468b37dbbf38b442384008c50d5727a3e",
      "parameters": [],
      "source_package": "einstein_gravity",
      "version": "4.0.0",
      "metadata": null
    },
    {
      "id": "github:einstein_gravity::general_relativity__gr_light_deflection",
      "type": "claim",
      "visibility": "public",
      "content": "广义相对论预测：光线掠过太阳表面时偏折   1.75'' 。",
      "content_hash": "0cba1988c016a3731480ca00ef6769370a495775a98f701dd73e684dd190840a",
